'@@author RishabhShenoy03
@startuml
title /value Sequence

actor User
participant Ui
participant CG2StocksTracker
participant Parser
participant PortfolioBook
participant Portfolio

User -> Ui : /value
Ui -> CG2StocksTracker : command text
CG2StocksTracker -> Parser : parse(...)
Parser --> CG2StocksTracker : VALUE
CG2StocksTracker -> PortfolioBook : getActivePortfolio()
PortfolioBook --> CG2StocksTracker : Portfolio
CG2StocksTracker -> Ui : showPortfolioValue(portfolio)
@enduml
